Dialogue: 10,0:00:09.73,0:00:10.99,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Kichijoji, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:11.65,0:00:14.91,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Azuki lives way out in Hachioji, and \Nthat's still another 30 minutes on the train.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:16.03,0:00:17.46,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,It really is far.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:24.87,0:00:27.07,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Well, we are 10th graders.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:27.07,0:00:28.34,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,And it's summer vacation.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:29.17,0:00:31.72,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,And it's Shuujin, so it's just a change of pace—
Dialogue: 10,0:00:32.52,0:00:33.12,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,But—
Dialogue: 10,0:00:33.47,0:00:34.97,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,he is writing the name, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.30,0:00:39.26,Niizuma,,0,0,0,,{\pos(660,217.269)\blur0.669}Niizuma
Dialogue: 10,0:00:39.26,0:00:40.44,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Niizuma Eiji.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:41.64,0:00:43.27,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,I should be able to gain something from this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.64,0:00:48.90,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can you see the blue bird,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.64,0:00:48.90,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,aozora tobikau Blue Bird
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.90,0:00:53.11,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,fluttering through the blue sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.90,0:00:53.11,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,ano tori ga miemasu ka?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.11,0:01:01.04,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,Happiness can't be described by a visible color, but I can feel
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.11,0:01:01.04,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,shiawase wa itsumo mienai Color kanjiteiru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.04,0:01:06.67,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1800)}Your love
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.63,0:01:18.55,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,On the inside of the sleeve of the shirt you gave me,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.63,0:01:18.55,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,kimi ga kureta shiroi SHATSU sodeguchi no ura
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.55,0:01:26.60,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,the word "FIGHT!" was embroidered in white
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.55,0:01:26.60,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,shiroi shishuu de tsuzurareta "FIGHT!" no gomoji
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.72,0:01:23.72,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.60,0:01:35.07,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,Even though I tried so hard by myself
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.60,0:01:35.07,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,mou hitori demo ganbareru ki de ita
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.07,0:01:43.41,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,890)}I wonder why my tears still fall?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.07,0:01:43.41,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,890)}doushite namida ga deru no darou?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.00,0:01:46.33,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,Your love
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.33,0:01:54.55,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll entrust myself to the wind since we are connected
