Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.55,0:01:57.76,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,I will walk
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.55,0:01:57.76,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,aruite yukeru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.76,0:02:02.06,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,now there's power in my chest, because I
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.76,0:02:02.06,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,shinjiru Power kono mune ni
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.06,0:02:05.52,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1550)}Believe your love
