Dialogue: 10,0:02:12.23,0:02:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you Mashiro?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:13.31,0:02:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, uh—
Dialogue: 10,0:02:14.32,0:02:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:14.98,0:02:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Nakai.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:16.34,0:02:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:17.43,0:02:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:19.61,0:02:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a bit noisy, but come on in.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:21.83,0:02:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:24.08,0:02:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Danger!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:25.15,0:02:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Danger!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:26.16,0:02:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:28.27,0:02:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Niizuma-sensei.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:29.34,0:02:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Mashiro is here.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:32.46,0:02:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you go introduce yourself.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:34.43,0:02:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,R—Right.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:37.59,0:02:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,My name's Mashiro.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:38.88,0:02:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm your new assistant starting today.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:40.89,0:02:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to working with you.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:42.36,0:02:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hello Mechadoc.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:44.68,0:02:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:45.19,0:02:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that too old?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:46.22,0:02:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Mechadocrow!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:47.99,0:02:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Mechacrow!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:48.89,0:02:50.85,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,What's up Mechadoc?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:52.51,0:02:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Niizuma-sensei is like that whenever he's not sleeping or eating.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:56.94,0:02:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And when he does sleep, he \Nwon't wake up for 20 hours.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:59.78,0:03:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:01.70,0:03:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Nakai.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:02.80,0:03:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop referring \Nto Niizuma as 'sensei'.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:06.29,0:03:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You are 17 years older than he is.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:08.58,0:03:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Fukuda. He started yesterday.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:10.83,0:03:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He's been in the running \Nfor the Tezuka Award twice.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:13.75,0:03:14.54,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Fukuda?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:14.54,0:03:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He's got the same editor as Niizuma-sensei, \Nand is working on getting serialized.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:21.01,0:03:22.18,Tezuka Award,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,0)\an8\bord0.669\b1\c&H1E222B&\3c&H1E222B&\frx7\pos(753.333,401.111)\fs33.426\blur1.003}Fukuda Shinta (18) Tokyo
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.01,0:03:22.18,Tezuka Award,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,0)\an8\bord4.011\b1\c&HA9C7EE&\3c&HA9C7EE&\frx7\pos(753.333,401.111)\fs33.426\blur1.003}Fukuda Shinta (18) Tokyo
Dialogue: 10,0:03:21.34,0:03:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that him?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:23.30,0:03:24.90,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure he was in Next with us.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:26.26,0:03:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:27.52,0:03:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Likewise.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:31.19,0:03:32.15,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,He's writing a name!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:32.15,0:03:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We end up having quite a bit of free time here
Dialogue: 10,0:03:34.62,0:03:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,so Fukuda uses all of his to \Nwrite names trying to get serialized.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:39.24,0:03:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure is impressive.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:40.61,0:03:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't need three assistants.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:42.99,0:03:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Niizuma ends up drawing \Nmost of the backgrounds,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:45.62,0:03:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,so that leaves us with just the \Ninking, whiteout, and screentone.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:48.41,0:03:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we get paid just for being here, \Nand transportation and meals are free.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:52.13,0:03:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And the place is air conditioned, \Nso I guess you can't complain.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:54.63,0:03:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Mashiro, you're better off \Nfinding your own thing to do too.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:57.55,0:03:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Mashiro, have you won any awards?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.40,0:04:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I haven't won any yet.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:02.55,0:04:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I've only been in Next once.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:05.35,0:04:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Recently?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:06.64,0:04:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a one-shot called "Money and Intelligence" printed last May.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:09.07,0:04:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That was you?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:09.93,0:04:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The 15-year-old genius, Ashirogi Muto—
Dialogue: 10,0:04:12.50,0:04:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So Ashirogi Muto was a pen-name, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:14.06,0:04:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.01,0:04:16.91,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,First a genius high-schooler,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:16.91,0:04:19.40,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,and now a 15-year-old genius, too?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:19.40,0:04:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that means I lost.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:21.95,0:04:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You were third, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.61,0:04:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I came in fifth.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:25.62,0:04:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad a real rival has shown up.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:29.24,0:04:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It sure is something to come up with an \Nidea like "Money and Intelligence" at 15.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:33.71,0:04:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But the tone and style wasn't right for Jack.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:36.46,0:04:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It was too realistic.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:38.67,0:04:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's only so much you \Ncan do with a story like that.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:41.33,0:04:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think it could make it to the top of Jack
Dialogue: 10,0:04:44.84,0:04:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But I guess I probably just \Nsound like a sore loser to you.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:48.47,0:04:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty soon, though, I'll be the new face of Jack.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:53.23,0:04:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Twice, Niizuma cheated \Nme out of the Tezuka award.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:58.52,0:05:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be sure to get into Jack and \Nreturn the favor with my pen!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:02.19,0:05:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that means Nakai \Nis at the bottom here, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:05.66,0:05:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,All he's done is win the monthly \Naward once about 10 years back.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:09.16,0:05:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If he's gonna keep calling Niizuma 'sensei,'
Dialogue: 10,0:05:10.96,0:05:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,we should have him do the same for us.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:14.96,0:05:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a joke.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:17.13,0:05:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just planning on being a pro assi, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:20.17,0:05:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,A pro assi?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:21.50,0:05:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, a professional assistant.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:23.42,0:05:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm still—
Dialogue: 10,0:05:24.93,0:05:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:25.63,0:05:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still thinking about getting serialized?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:27.72,0:05:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're already getting old
Dialogue: 10,0:05:29.23,0:05:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and I never see you working \Non anything in your free time.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:31.97,0:05:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Even Yujiro said that he isn't \Nexpecting anything more from you.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:36.04,0:05:39.16,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,There's no way I'm gonna let myself end up like that.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:36.52,0:05:39.16,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,I'm supposed to work in this atmosphere?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:39.56,0:05:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I haven't explained \Nhow things work yet, have I?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:42.70,0:05:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,First, we take the manuscript pages \Nthat Niizuma-sensei puts on the floor
Dialogue: 10,0:05:45.41,0:05:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and do inking and screentones.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:47.29,0:05:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we put them back exactly where we found them.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:49.59,0:05:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,An 'X' means inking
Dialogue: 10,0:05:50.88,0:05:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,and screentone shades are written in blue.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:53.15,0:05:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:54.09,0:05:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,For now, just sit here
Dialogue: 10,0:05:55.60,0:05:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and wait for Niizuma-sensei to \Nput the next page on the floor.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:59.54,0:06:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Um,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:00.75,0:06:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,would it be alright if I \Nwatched Niizuma for awhile?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:03.45,0:06:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not worth your time.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:04.66,0:06:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Not worth?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:05.21,0:06:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Niizuma doesn't have much experience yet.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:07.94,0:06:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And besides, he's not about to teach you anything.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:11.14,0:06:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't expect him to teach me anything.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:13.06,0:06:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to watch him.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:14.93,0:06:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,He's got the best drawings out of any of us here.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:17.69,0:06:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, I just don't get youngsters these days.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:21.12,0:06:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And they sure are rude.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:22.45,0:06:23.23,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Same goes for you!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:23.23,0:06:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You c-c-c-crow!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:27.86,0:06:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show you my power.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:30.19,0:06:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:30.91,0:06:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Vanishing point!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:33.87,0:06:36.54,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Is that how he decides on a vanishing point?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:36.54,0:06:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Dark clouds! Dark clouds! Dark \Nclouds! Dark clouds! Dark clouds!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:41.79,0:06:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me for a moment.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:43.42,0:06:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You are in my way.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:48.17,0:06:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfect!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:55.64,0:06:58.68,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,So I just take this and put it back when I'm done?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:59.15,0:06:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:00.10,0:07:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ashirogi-sensei!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:01.65,0:07:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:02.36,0:07:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,'Sensei?'
Dialogue: 10,0:07:03.69,0:07:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.82,0:07:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here to be your assistant.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:08.11,0:07:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:09.18,0:07:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd much rather you work \Non your own manga instead.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:14.45,0:07:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I wanted to,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:15.54,0:07:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,we haven't come up with a story yet.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:17.33,0:07:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:18.47,0:07:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though you came up with something\Nas great as "Money and Intelligence?"
Dialogue: 10,0:07:21.58,0:07:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The one in charge of writing the stories is Takagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:24.59,0:07:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Mashiro, the one in charge of the drawings.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:25.93,0:07:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, so that's how you do it?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:29.17,0:07:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I must say, Takagi-sensei sure is talented.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:33.39,0:07:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:34.80,0:07:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So while he's thinking of a story,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:37.07,0:07:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd come here and see if there \Nwasn't anything I could learn from you.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:39.68,0:07:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there really anything you could learn from me?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:42.90,0:07:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably—
Dialogue: 10,0:07:44.19,0:07:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,If you'll let me watch you draw.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:46.36,0:07:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a seat, then.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:48.24,0:07:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be more comfortable that way, Ashirogi-sensei.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:51.12,0:07:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you're the sensei here.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:53.49,0:07:57.08,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Even so, I'm so glad we were able to meet again.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:54.62,0:07:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,They seem close.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:56.70,0:08:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I really don't get youngsters these days.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:57.08,0:08:00.00,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Please make yourself at home.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:02.87,0:08:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want melon or chocolate?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:04.50,0:08:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine with whatever.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:06.22,0:08:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.55,0:08:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:08.39,0:08:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,How does it look?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:09.51,0:08:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Woah!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:10.84,0:08:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You've already written this much?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:12.72,0:08:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.02,0:08:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess that's to be expected of a manga writer.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:16.14,0:08:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Still not finished with my own name yet, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:24.02,0:08:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Saiko went to be an assistant—
Dialogue: 10,0:08:27.44,0:08:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it strange for him to just be an assistant?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:31.07,0:08:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,He's supposed to be your partner.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:33.40,0:08:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't go with him because I can't draw,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:36.20,0:08:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'd rather him get something done
Dialogue: 10,0:08:38.53,0:08:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,than just sit around waiting \Nfor me to finish the story.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:43.25,0:08:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Saiko's drawings already pass as a pro's.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:48.22,0:08:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:49.09,0:08:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What you said back then was right.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:51.67,0:08:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't as easy as I thought \Nto become number one.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:54.72,0:08:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:55.36,0:08:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Even with a first chapter like that?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:56.51,0:08:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The first chapter came in first,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:58.61,0:09:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,but chapter two came in fourth.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:00.23,0:09:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I was shocked.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:01.27,0:09:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Fourth place is still great!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:03.08,0:09:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The first chapter is fresh and has color pages,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:05.28,0:09:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,so it's not uncommon to get first place.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.69,0:09:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,They say that even if you \Nget first on the first chapter,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:09.37,0:09:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,the hard part starts with chapter two.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:11.16,0:09:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Yujiro said the same thing.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:13.49,0:09:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of new stories' second chapters \Ndrop way down in the ranking.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:17.16,0:09:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're still up in the ranks of popular\Nmanga that already have anime series.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:20.12,0:09:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing wrong with that.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:22.46,0:09:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He said that, too, but—
Dialogue: 10,0:09:24.30,0:09:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're even good enough to write \Na manuscript without doing a name,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:27.89,0:09:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,so I don't think you'll drop \Nany further in the rankings.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:30.55,0:09:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You usually need to submit the first three\Nchapters for the serialization meetings,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:32.89,0:09:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,but you can take as much time \Nas you want to make them.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:36.01,0:09:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That means it gets harder \Nstarting with chapter four,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:38.15,0:09:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,but you don't need to worry about that.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:40.04,0:09:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that so?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:41.67,0:09:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hearing you say that gives me more confidence.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:45.06,0:09:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You can easily keep up a high ranking.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:47.45,0:09:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Do that for a year or so, get an anime, \Nand that'll bump you up to first.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:49.94,0:09:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:51.03,0:09:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,An anime will bump me up to first?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.79,0:09:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:53.44,0:09:54.15,Default-Alt2,,0,0,0,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:54.15,0:09:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, your rank will continue to drop!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:56.03,0:09:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:57.13,0:09:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Fukuda?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.53,0:10:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Your 10-week trial run'll be fine,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.07,0:10:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,but you'll be cancelled in six months!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:03.29,0:10:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Cancelled?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:04.37,0:10:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I thought while I \Nread chapters three, four, and five.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:08.57,0:10:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:09.72,0:10:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to get cancelled.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:10.89,0:10:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Please show me chapters four and five!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:15.51,0:10:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,How are they?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:17.01,0:10:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I think they're amazing, as usual.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:20.39,0:10:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,This makes them really easy to read.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:24.52,0:10:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But when you get to chapters three, \Nfour, and five, you get used to it
Dialogue: 10,0:10:28.07,0:10:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,so I feel like it starts to wear off a little.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:30.31,0:10:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:31.81,0:10:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,'Amazing' and 'interesting' are two different things.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:34.36,0:10:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If the readers don't think it's \Ninteresting, then your popularity will fall.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:38.11,0:10:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So what should I do?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:39.60,0:10:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe write it so that it's \Nmore fun for the readers.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:42.16,0:10:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And maybe make it a little easier to read.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:44.15,0:10:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds good.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:45.29,0:10:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Niizuma, you need to be more aware \Nnow that you've become a pro mangaka.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:48.59,0:10:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If you just want to draw \Nmanga that you like drawing,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:50.72,0:10:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,then make doujinshi.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:52.67,0:10:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're a pro in Jack now.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:55.21,0:10:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to think about \Nwhat the readers want first.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:58.72,0:11:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And "Crow" doesn't have \Nanything the readers can relate to.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:02.18,0:11:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It just looks cool.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:03.43,0:11:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And that will cause people to get bored quickly.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:05.18,0:11:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It just looks cool?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:06.79,0:11:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Ashirogi-sensei has \Nyou beat in that respect.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:08.77,0:11:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,"Money and Intelligence" was interesting, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:12.65,0:11:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:13.61,0:11:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's interesting because it \Nmakes people ask the question
Dialogue: 10,0:11:18.54,0:11:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,"What if the real world really is just like this?"
Dialogue: 10,0:11:21.36,0:11:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:22.88,0:11:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Mine doesn't have anything like that.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:26.04,0:11:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Your drawing ability is definitely genius-level.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:29.54,0:11:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're still at the level \Nwhere you're just excited
Dialogue: 10,0:11:32.64,0:11:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,about the editing department calling you a genius.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:35.17,0:11:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,At least, that's my opinion.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:37.38,0:11:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's amazing, Fukuda.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:39.38,0:11:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You're even better than the editors.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:40.75,0:11:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:41.47,0:11:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Most people aiming to be a mangaka \Nshould be able to give this level of criticism.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:45.13,0:11:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,They just can't write anything \Ninteresting themselves.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:47.62,0:11:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's not true for me, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:49.03,0:11:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it now!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:50.60,0:11:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll rewrite chapter five in the \Ntwo days left before the deadline!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:53.66,0:11:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Please help me to make it more interesting!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:56.27,0:11:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:57.52,0:11:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You're joking, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:59.19,0:12:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would I help out a rival?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:01.03,0:12:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You give amazing advice!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:03.96,0:12:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't mean that—
Dialogue: 10,0:12:05.57,0:12:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, why am I even giving advice?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:09.54,0:12:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, I want to try.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:11.04,0:12:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Mashiro?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:13.00,0:12:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to help figure out
Dialogue: 10,0:12:15.92,0:12:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,what would be best for "Crow."
Dialogue: 10,0:12:28.43,0:12:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:29.77,0:12:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm only helping with chapter five.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:32.09,0:12:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The three of us will work on it together.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:34.52,0:12:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That good enough?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:35.36,0:12:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.27,0:12:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,At first, I thought you were a bad person,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:39.32,0:12:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,but you're actually pretty nice, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.16,0:12:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not a nice person!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:41.41,0:12:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We are going to change Jack!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:44.03,0:12:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I just don't want my rivals to fail so early!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:47.87,0:12:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so cool!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:49.61,0:12:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We are going to change Jack!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:51.45,0:12:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,At any rate, let's put this chapter at the top.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:54.02,0:12:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:55.21,0:12:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:56.13,0:12:58.38,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,What's with these guys?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:58.38,0:12:59.51,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Their youth?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:59.51,0:13:02.19,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,No, they've got determination and skill.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:03.26,0:13:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what should I do to make \Nchapter five more interesting?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:07.09,0:13:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's felt the same since chapter one,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:09.99,0:13:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,so maybe add some variation?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:11.90,0:13:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:12.89,0:13:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,All you do is focus on Crow in every chapter.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:16.56,0:13:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,More than half of new series \Ndisappear in less than a year.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:20.73,0:13:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The first 10 chapters will determine whether \Nor not a series can last in the long run.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:24.78,0:13:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, you should focus on \Ndrawing in as many readers as you can.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:28.82,0:13:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yujiro said that to you too, didn't he?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:30.53,0:13:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't mention it.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:32.65,0:13:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What's he doing telling me and not you \Nwhen I haven't even been serialized yet?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:37.33,0:13:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,"Let's just say that we're having \Nmeetings about the names."
Dialogue: 10,0:13:40.31,0:13:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,is what he told me.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:42.50,0:13:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is he thinking?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:45.09,0:13:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't he just doing that because he \Nbelieves in Niizuma's ability?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:48.43,0:13:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:49.39,0:13:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a bit frustrated when I \Ntold him I didn't want to do it,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:52.53,0:13:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,but he finally caved.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:54.60,0:13:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,An editor who doesn't have meetings \Nand a writer who doesn't do names.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:57.91,0:13:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you guys even taking this seriously?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:59.69,0:14:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I do a name, I feel like I'm doing \Nthe same thing twice and it's not as fun.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:05.37,0:14:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's such a hassle.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:06.53,0:14:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't have a meeting
Dialogue: 10,0:14:07.87,0:14:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and you don't submit a name,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:09.19,0:14:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,there's no way your editor can judge \Nif your chapter is interesting or not!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:11.91,0:14:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet you still ask us how \Nto make it more interesting?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:14.84,0:14:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop screwing around!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:16.12,0:14:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:17.25,0:14:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So how do you think I can make it more interesting,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:20.59,0:14:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Fukuda-sensei?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:23.21,0:14:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What, so now you call me 'sensei'?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:25.11,0:14:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the first time I met you was \Nat the Tezuka Award Ceremony
Dialogue: 10,0:14:29.02,0:14:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and you hadn't debuted in Next \Nyet, so I called you Fukuda.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:32.89,0:14:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But, now that you've debuted, you're Fukuda-sensei.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:34.85,0:14:37.78,Default-Alt2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nobody cares about that right now.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:35.68,0:14:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I call everybody who's debuted 'sensei'.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:39.10,0:14:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So I guess that means the only one \Nhere who's not a 'sensei' is Nakai.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:45.32,0:14:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's too bad.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:46.32,0:14:47.53,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:47.53,0:14:49.76,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,You're saying that in front of him?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:49.76,0:14:50.87,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,And laughing?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:52.24,0:14:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,At any rate!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:53.45,0:14:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't just write what's fun for you,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:55.20,0:14:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,but think about the readers, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:56.95,0:14:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, think about the readers, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:59.71,0:15:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe something with more suspense?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:03.38,0:15:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:04.63,0:15:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to create a climax
Dialogue: 10,0:15:06.89,0:15:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and end the chapter so that \Nthe readers want to read more.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:09.39,0:15:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:10.26,0:15:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Suspenseful!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:11.19,0:15:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Exciting!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:11.98,0:15:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Thrilling!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:13.39,0:15:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Climax!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:14.40,0:15:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Cliffhangers!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:15.31,0:15:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Unpredictability!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:16.90,0:15:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We never said unpredictable.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:18.77,0:15:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But it'd be better with it.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:21.27,0:15:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:22.56,0:15:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The answer isn't in the ink,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.11,0:15:28.61,TLNote,,0,0,0,,Note: The word "beta" means "cliché," but is also used for "inking" manga.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:24.06,0:15:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,but in a cliché story!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:25.66,0:15:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Cliché and unpredictability are one and the same.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:28.60,0:15:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So exciting!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:29.53,0:15:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's always the same if he \Njust beats them every time!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:33.74,0:15:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Change the enemy character.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:34.84,0:15:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Make him stronger.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:36.13,0:15:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, he's really an ally?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:37.46,0:15:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And pull in the readers.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:38.50,0:15:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:39.30,0:15:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that's good.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:40.41,0:15:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It sure is cliché,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:41.84,0:15:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's a plot twist that'll attract attention.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:43.64,0:15:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Standby.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:44.63,0:15:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Music—
Dialogue: 10,0:15:45.29,0:15:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Start!!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:48.67,0:15:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't just start with the manuscript!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:50.84,0:15:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But I hate names.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:52.23,0:15:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Well that's too bad!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:54.51,0:15:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,After giving all that advice,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:55.98,0:15:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,we have the right to see if it's interesting or not.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:00.02,0:16:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever you say.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:07.19,0:16:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Gachapin!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:08.24,0:16:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Green monster.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:11.70,0:16:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm finished.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.45,0:16:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,19 pages sure goes fast.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:14.57,0:16:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my line!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:15.46,0:16:16.35,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,It's no good.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:16.35,0:16:20.00,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,He's so fast that I can't analyze how \Nhe thinks or plans anything out.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:23.54,0:16:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:24.92,0:16:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's a lot better.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:26.84,0:16:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Tada! Standby on the music!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:34.93,0:16:36.90,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,He did all this with just that much advice
Dialogue: 10,0:16:36.90,0:16:38.54,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,and in this short amount of time?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:39.06,0:16:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess he's a genius in more ways than one.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:42.60,0:16:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be sure to overtake him, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:44.77,0:16:46.74,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,But since he is a genius,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:47.23,0:16:49.74,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,that means there's definitely \Nsomething I can learn from this.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:50.36,0:16:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So Mashiro, why don't you \Nwrite your manga by yourself?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:53.61,0:16:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:54.66,0:16:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,From what I've seen, it looks like you're \Npretty knowledgeable about manga.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:58.49,0:17:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If you work in a pair, you only get half the money.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:01.37,0:17:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've heard it's pretty tough, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:03.04,0:17:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we're a team.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:05.50,0:17:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,My partner is a lot better than \NI am at coming up with stories.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:10.25,0:17:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm taking off.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:12.26,0:17:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Niizuma-sensei!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:12.98,0:17:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You look like you're busy rewriting \Nthe chapter, so I'm leaving for today.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:16.09,0:17:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be back tomorrow at three.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:17.86,0:17:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:19.12,0:17:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I should have the first half done by then.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:21.52,0:17:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and Ashirogi-sensei, Nakai, you won't have \Nanything else to do until tomorrow afternoon, either.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:26.40,0:17:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,One more thing.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:27.48,0:17:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us do the backgrounds.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:29.90,0:17:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,If you've got time to draw \Nthe backgrounds and effects,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:32.04,0:17:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,you should be using it to \Nthink more about your story.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:36.24,0:17:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But, aren't I the write-from-instinct type?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:39.12,0:17:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I think your manga will get better
Dialogue: 10,0:17:42.02,0:17:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,if you spend more time \Nthinking about the story, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:44.54,0:17:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And we've got Nakai here, as well.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:47.79,0:17:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He's been an assistant for more than 10 years.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:50.92,0:17:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's just the background, \Nhe can draw more than you.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.87,0:17:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,His technique is amazing, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:55.80,0:17:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Nakai?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:57.43,0:18:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I can draw anything and any place
Dialogue: 10,0:18:00.40,0:18:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,from any angle you need without a reference.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:03.10,0:18:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Background effects,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:03.78,0:18:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,inking,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:04.65,0:18:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,screentones—
Dialogue: 10,0:18:05.56,0:18:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody's faster than me.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:07.51,0:18:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think that's something somebody who's \Naiming to get serialized should be bragging about.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:13.03,0:18:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright then, I've gotta get \Nhome and get some sleep.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:15.80,0:18:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got a part time job, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:17.01,0:18:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,A part-time job?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:17.65,0:18:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, an early morning job at a convenient store.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:19.96,0:18:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't survive on just being an assistant.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:21.96,0:18:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, I'll end up as one of two things:
Dialogue: 10,0:18:24.16,0:18:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,either a free-lance artist or a mangaka.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:25.75,0:18:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:27.96,0:18:29.60,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't tell just by looking,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:29.60,0:18:31.14,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,but he's actually a pretty hard worker.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:32.17,0:18:33.14,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Niizuma Eiji.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:33.71,0:18:34.60,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Fukuda Shinta.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:35.42,0:18:37.31,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,I want to go up against them both in Jack.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:38.30,0:18:41.15,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,But it's too naive to think that \Nall of us will get serialized.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:42.26,0:18:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Mashiro, you want to get some dinner?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:44.32,0:18:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,S—Sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:47.98,0:18:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have the steak set with a side of \Nfried chicken, carpaccio, and french fries.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:53.65,0:18:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And a banana parfait for dessert.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:55.49,0:18:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and a cream soda.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:57.74,0:18:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Mashiro, just order whatever you like.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:59.70,0:19:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,R—Right.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:01.45,0:19:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Niizuma-sensei is pretty generous.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:04.05,0:19:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as we have a receipt, he \Nsaid we can eat whatever we like.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:07.09,0:19:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:09.37,0:19:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Mashiro,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:10.48,0:19:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,are you staying the night?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:11.54,0:19:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:12.92,0:19:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd planned on working all night, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:15.13,0:19:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:15.93,0:19:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Still young, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:17.34,0:19:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just getting started, aren't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:21.14,0:19:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We're back.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:24.68,0:19:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,He wears headphones at night, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:26.68,0:19:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Only because his editor told him that he had to.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:29.81,0:19:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a break room if you want to hit the sack.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:32.27,0:19:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:32.81,0:19:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to stay up with Niizuma for a bit.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:57.55,0:19:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to get serialized—
Dialogue: 10,0:20:02.26,0:20:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,S—Sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:04.05,0:20:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:05.60,0:20:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I understand what it feels like.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:08.81,0:20:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That kind of makes it worse.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:11.81,0:20:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,S—Sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:13.98,0:20:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd probably be better for me to just give\Nup and become a professional assistant.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:20.86,0:20:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But I just can't give up on my \Ndream of being a mangaka.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:23.91,0:20:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, all I do is waste my time going \Nfrom one assistant job to the next.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:28.12,0:20:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I'm already 33.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:30.37,0:20:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever you do,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:32.21,0:20:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,don't let yourself get stuck \Nbeing an assistant forever.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:39.92,0:20:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:47.68,0:20:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:49.06,0:20:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:51.43,0:20:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Crow!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:52.03,0:20:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,C—Crow!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:53.77,0:20:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:55.85,0:20:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He's already done this much?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:56.94,0:20:58.57,Default-Alt2,,0,0,0,,Black wings!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:57.40,0:20:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no background!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:59.32,0:21:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally some real work to do.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:01.69,0:21:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We're about to get busy.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:02.87,0:21:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:05.03,0:21:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Last three!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:12.12,0:21:13.81,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:13.81,0:21:19.09,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Nakai is drawing such a complicated background\N freehand and then going over it with the pen.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:24.76,0:21:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:26.02,0:21:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:27.28,0:21:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:28.27,0:21:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Afternoon.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:29.39,0:21:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Niizuma,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:30.23,0:21:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,which of these is chapter five?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:32.13,0:21:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,There's so many I can't tell.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:33.49,0:21:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's not ready yet, so leave it.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:35.58,0:21:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Not ready?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:36.60,0:21:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But you said on the phone the day before\Nyesterday that you were already finished.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:38.94,0:21:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm rewriting it.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:40.47,0:21:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:41.90,0:21:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the chapter five name.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:43.24,0:21:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Name?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:44.28,0:21:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You wrote a name?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:47.16,0:21:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:48.58,0:21:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This is really great!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:49.99,0:21:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it really?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:51.59,0:21:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's amazing!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:53.62,0:21:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yujiro,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:54.79,0:21:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for being so rude up until now.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:56.89,0:21:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have meetings from now on.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:58.63,0:22:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll write the names, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:00.71,0:22:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,W—What happened?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:02.55,0:22:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody kept calling me a genius, \Nso I guess I got a bit conceited.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:06.17,0:22:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:07.72,0:22:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do all that, it'd sure \Ntake a load off my mind.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:11.47,0:22:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep it up and becoming the best \Nwriter in Jack won't be just a dream.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:15.56,0:22:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a dream?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:17.52,0:22:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The early results for chapter three have you in—
Dialogue: 10,0:22:19.28,0:22:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,third!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:20.06,0:22:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's better than chapter two.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:22.07,0:22:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Chapter three is better?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:24.34,0:22:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess we were wrong, then.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:26.44,0:22:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't regret it, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:29.13,0:22:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We helped him make chapter five even better
Dialogue: 10,0:22:30.83,0:22:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and got him to start having \Nmeetings and writing names.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:35.12,0:22:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:36.34,0:22:39.63,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna become the most \Npopular mangaka out there!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:37.83,0:22:41.21,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,I'm glad he got Eiji to start writing names.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:42.88,0:22:44.68,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,I came here for Shuujin.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:45.46,0:22:47.43,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,I'll make sure to learn something before I go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.34,0:22:56.27,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,I always wondered "Why am I the only one having a hard time?"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.34,0:22:56.27,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,doushite boku dake ga kon'nani tsurai no ka to itsumo omotteta
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.06,0:23:01.73,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,The people around me all seemed so happy
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.06,0:23:01.73,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,mawari no hito bakari shiawase sou ni mieta
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.19,0:23:09.24,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,But when I talked to you, I felt just a little bit better
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.19,0:23:09.24,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,dakedo kimi to hanashitara sukoshi dakedakedo ki ga raku ni natta
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.03,0:23:14.74,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's because we were open with each other
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.03,0:23:14.74,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,nita youna koto uchiakete kuretakara kana
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.58,0:23:22.25,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sometimes the reality you can't see with your eyes is like a monster
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.58,0:23:22.25,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,kao no mienai genjitsu ga toki ni kaibutsu no you ni
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.25,0:23:29.51,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,Our ambitions are crushed, but we move on
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.25,0:23:29.51,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,bokura no kokorozashi wo tsubusou to oshiyosete kurukeredo
